good.tweet: Weekend dey come, e go madt!
Today gym don make me feel strong.
I dey look forward to my next project.
Just read one correct blog on top web development.
I just finish one better book, e sweet.
This new season of my favorite show dey burst my head.
Chop better lunch today, I no fit complain.
Just start to learn new programming language, e dey interesting.
I dey feel inspired to do new things.

bad.tweet: Monday no dey ever sweet, na wah for life.
Everything just dey go wrong today, wahala no dey finish.
This project don tire me, e no dey gree work.
This weather no make sense at all, e too bad.
I no get any ginger today, e weak me.
Today na the worst day wey I don ever see.
I feel like to just give up, e don do.
